﻿Release notes for BRCA Exchange data Version 1, dated October 6, 2016


These data consist of a re-analysis of the Version 0 BRCA Exchange data, which were originally built manually, and released in April 2016.   They include variant data from 1000 Genomes, BIC, ClinVar, ESP, ExAC, exLOVD, LOVD and ENIGMA.  This re-analysis of the previous data was performed with an automated Luigi pipeline, running software from https://github.com/BD2KGenomics/brca-exchange/tree/master/pipeline/luigi commit ID f8e675e2459df4c22694184ee0daf0af9a0bfe64.


Known issues:
* The number of variants reported does not equal the expected number (13500).  We are looking into this.


To report new issues: please email brcaexchange@gmail.com.
